    {
      "id": "21a44c6c-c51d-432c-afb9-d348a84d7412",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MOOC success requires great amounts of SR skills. Authors look to understand self-regulated learning behaviors in n online chemistry course and a high percentage of first-generation students. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "21a44c6c-c51d-432c-afb9-d348a84d7412",
        "parent": {
