    {
      "id": "9bf379b0-950c-4202-ae8c-2cc4fd75c707",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Mapping clustering to first generation status, the authors found that First-Gen students with planning behaviors perform just as well as non first-gen. However, Firt-generation low engagement students were the lowest performing students. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "9bf379b0-950c-4202-ae8c-2cc4fd75c707",
        "parent": {
